Comment: I've not been practicing anything for about a month but I've been doing some Roux solves for fun.  This Ao5 was pretty consistent and possibly my first Roux solves on camera, all 26 to 28 second solves with a mean of 27.45.  I'm not planning to switch method completely as it would be way too much effort to match to my CFOP times with a new method.  Maybe I'll work towards sub-20 with the Roux method...
